{"tid":1134692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[厲害了我的国] 華為高層自稱手機銷量已經超越三星蘋果位居世界第一","createTime":"2019-05-02T00:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T03:30:34.000Z","uid":155095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"46b483339b5eab0aad62a014e7d3c2b34bac954d","tid":1134692,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:00:19.000Z","msg":"2019年3月27日，網傳一份德國權威機構GfK的統計數據顯示，今年1月，華為及其旗下榮耀的海外智能手機銷量逆勢上揚，<strong>華為排名第一</strong>。不過當天GfK即出面<strong>闢謠指數據為偽造</strong>。陸媒披露，這份數據<strong>來自華為兩名高管</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2019/03/GettyImages-1012367468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FGettyImages-1012367468.jpg&h=1e4892d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據中國一家財經類媒體報導，27日，華為公司<ins>副董事長郭平</ins>和華為消費者業務<ins>CEO余承東</ins>在朋友圈和好友群中，分享了題為「GfK-2019年1月全球手機市場銷量排名」及「GfK-2019年1月海外手機市場（不含中國）銷量排名」的圖片，並慶賀「2019年1月華為手機銷量全球登頂」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2019/03/0ccadd7260d9f6359c564b15a8557db4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F0ccadd7260d9f6359c564b15a8557db4.jpg&h=ef90ae90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片中的數據顯示，當月全球智能手機市場容量5,908萬台，同比下降27%。海外智能手機市場容量2,851萬台，同比下降35%。同時，包括三星、蘋果在內的大部份手機廠商出貨量都大幅下滑，只有華為及其旗下榮耀的銷量逆勢上揚，而且華為出貨量高舉榜首。<br />\n<br />\n捷孚凱諮詢（GfK，消費者調查公司）是一家德國市場研究公司，一直是業內所認可的數據調研權威機構。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2019/03/3A990FE906EAC337ED0712294FFF17A2630CD218_w524_h931.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F3A990FE906EAC337ED0712294FFF17A2630CD218_w524_h931.jpg&h=e04742b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨後，多家陸媒和港媒跟進報導了所謂「今年1月華為銷量第一」的消息。截至發稿時，網上仍有大量相關報導留存。<br />\n<br />\n不過，27日下午，GfK（中國）公司就發表了一份官方公告，宣布上述銷量數據並非該機構所發布，實為<span style=\"color: red;\">盜用GfK名義</span>。公告並警告可能對造假者<span style=\"color: red;\">採取法律行動</span>。<br />\n<br />\nGfK內部人員景輝也在朋友圈闢謠，公開嘲諷造假者「<span style=\"color: red;\">不會小學算數</span>」。<br />\n<br />\nGfK數據只推送給客戶，不對外公開。不過，為了說明網傳數據的虛假，景輝給出了GfK部份統計數據，即2019年1月中國手機市場智能手機銷售3057萬台，而中國手機市場占全球市場約23%的銷量。<br />\n<br />\n按此數據計算，1月全球智能手機銷量約為13,291萬台，海外手機銷量約10,234萬台，和網傳數據差距甚大。"},{"pid":"bd66e4ca70b9bb51b91679d2b0a6dd0cc6d30852","tid":1134692,"uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:05:54.000Z","msg":"造假認第二<br />\n都冇其他國家敢認第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n厲害了"},{"pid":"4dc9aa7b45b2fbab29667c852e828987d06851f4","tid":1134692,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:09:40.000Z","msg":"55ok"},{"pid":"efe30190063b4929da43ff1d0aebc1385a59cf8e","tid":1134692,"uid":229609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:16:37.000Z","msg":"理得佢銷量宇宙第一都好,關我撚事?<br />\n永遠不買大陸機!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f9961cfb72d2d09e24cf6e1d9708243403cba2","tid":1134692,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:23:43.000Z","msg":"瞓醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae9f1a1ab2f23499573e3f837b0beaccdcbbaad","tid":1134692,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:33:31.000Z","msg":"做假天下第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401956b09d509a1ab9842abb79027222c212b932","tid":1134692,"uid":244822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:39:29.000Z","msg":"已經做到咁撚大都淨係識得係個we7group度打飛機 造假呃下啲唔撚上網嘅廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21f898670c21010cf2a53bbce0f801cc2753458","tid":1134692,"uid":155095,"li